      <div class="row">
        <h2 class="head">Unique GCES Features Enable Registered Government Contractors to&#8230;</h2>
        <div class="medium-6 columns">
          <h3>Acquire Qualified Consultant Support Quickly</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Real-time access to ever-expanding nationwide database of consultants and mentors</li>
            <li>Extensive database search capabilities leading to quick, efficient selection of consultants</li>
            <li>Direct access to consultants for interviews, work requirements, and hourly rate negotiations</li>
            <li>Pre-negotiated master agreement enables consultants to start work immediately</li>
            <li>All consultants vetted for prior performance, citizenship, and personal liability issues</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="medium-6 columns">
          <h3>Reduce Corporate Overhead Costs</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Master Contract negotiated once with GCES</li>
            <li>Multiple consultant engagements managed via single contract</li>
            <li>Individual engagements managed via purchase orders</li>
            <li>GCES manages all consultant invoicing, payment &amp; tax processing</li>
            <li>GCES consultants incur no employee-related expenses</li>
            <li>Small fixed fee per consultant labor hour guarantees best-qualified consultants at affordable cost</li>
          </ul>
          <%= link_to 'Register as a Contractor', new_sales_lead_path %>
          <%= link_to 'More information? Contact us &#187;', contact_us_path %>
      </div>
    </li> 
  </ul>
</div>
